OL,3,CMinister seeks legal advice on law
OL,4,Cchange amid apartments controversy
OL,6,FA Stormont minister has sought urgent
OL,7,Flegal advice on changing legislation
OL,8,Fon defective buildings in Northern
OL,9,FIreland following a controversy around
OL,10,FVictoria Square apartments in Belfast.
OL,12,FDeputy First Minister Emma Little-
OL,13,FPengelly said her DUP colleague and
OL,14,FCommunities Minister Gordon Lyons was
OL,15,F"actively looking" at the potential
OL,16,Ffor changing the law and would be
OL,17,Freporting back to Executive colleagues
OL,18,F"very shortly".
