OL,4,Cchange amid apartments controversy
OL,6,FResidents of the apartment complex in
OL,7,FBelfast city centre left the premises
OL,8,Fin 2019 after structural issues were
OL,9,Ffound.
OL,11,FThey have called on Stormont to extend
OL,12,Fa statutory time limit to enable them
OL,13,Fto take a new compensation claim.
OL,15,FOn Wednesday, it was announced that
OL,16,Fresidents would be issued with refunds
OL,17,Ffor the rates bills they had paid
OL,18,Fduring the period when their
OL,19,Fproperties were uninhabitable.
