OL,6,FEarlier this month, a legal bid by the
OL,7,Fapartment owners was struck out in
OL,8,FBelfast High Court after the judge
OL,9,Fruled it fell outside the terms of
OL,10,Fexisting legislation that required
OL,11,Fclaims to be made within six years of
OL,12,Fthe property's construction.
OL,14,FThe case had been taken against
OL,15,Farchitects involved in the design and
OL,16,Ftwo building companies. All deny any
OL,17,Fliability.
