OL,6,FResidents had to leave the apartments
OL,7,Fin 2019 after a defect was identified
OL,8,Fin a structural column. They had been
OL,9,Funable to return, but ` in the years
OL,10,Fsince ` were still subject to paying
OL,11,Fcertain bills, such as rates, for
OL,12,Ftheir properties.
OL,14,FA charity, Ulster Garden Villages,
OL,15,Fowns 54 of the 91 apartments in
OL,16,FVictoria Square. The remaining
OL,17,Fproperties are owned by individuals.
