OL,6,FAfter the case was struck out,
OL,7,FAssembly members have faced calls to
OL,8,Fchange the law to extend the statutory
OL,9,Ftime limit to 30 years.
OL,11,FThe construction of the apartments,
OL,12,Fwhich sit above the Victoria Square
OL,13,Fshopping complex, was completed in
OL,14,F2008.
OL,16,FThe limit for claims was extended from
OL,17,Fsix years to 30 years in England and
OL,18,FWales two years ago.
