OL,6,FMs Little-Pengelly was asked about the
OL,7,Fissue during a visit to Lough Neagh on
OL,8,FWednesday.
OL,10,F"I think there's been an incredible
OL,11,Funfairness here," she said.
OL,13,F"I think we all feel that deep
OL,14,Funfairness to those that are impacted
OL,15,Fby this.
OL,17,F"Those people understandably want
OL,18,Faction very quickly."
