OL,6,FThe deputy First Minister said at last
OL,7,Fweek's Executive meeting, Finance
OL,8,FMinister Caoimhe Archibald and Mr
OL,9,FLyons were tasked with undertaking
OL,10,Ffurther work on the issue and
OL,11,Freporting back "urgently" to
OL,12,Fministerial colleagues.
OL,14,F"It will, as we understand it, require
OL,15,Flegislative change," she said.
OL,17,F"The Minister for Communities is
OL,18,Factively looking at this at the
OL,19,Fmoment, he's taking legal advice about
OL,20,Fthat.
