OL,6,F"He's very conscious of the timescales
OL,7,Fon this.
OL,9,F"So we are positive that we will have
OL,10,Fthat detailed advice to the Executive
OL,11,Fand to us very, very shortly in terms
OL,12,Fof what action we can take to support
OL,13,Fthose impacted by this unjustness."
