OL,6,FOn Wednesday, the minister welcomed an
OL,7,Fannouncement from Land and Property
OL,8,FServices that refunds worth a total of
OL,9,F#170,000 would be issued to residents
OL,10,Fcovering the period from April 2019.
OL,12,FThe properties would no longer be
OL,13,Fliable for future rates payments, and
OL,14,Frates arrears for non-payment of bills
OL,15,Fsince 2019 ` totalling around #396,000
OL,16,F` would no longer be pursued.
