OL,6,F"The owners of the Victoria Square
OL,7,FApartments have endured significant
OL,8,Fturmoil, having found themselves in a
OL,9,Fdifficult situation through no fault
OL,10,Fof their own," Ms Archibald said.
OL,12,F"I have been determined to find a way
OL,13,Fforward in respect of rates for the
OL,14,FVictoria Square Apartment ratepayers."
OL,16,FFirst Minister Michelle O'Neill said
OL,17,FExecutive ministers would do "whatever
OL,18,Fwe can" to help the residents.
OL,20,F"If it requires legislation, then
OL,21,Fthat's what we need to do," she said.
